      "x": 810,
      "y": 195,
      "width": 380,
      "height": 80,
      "text": "BCM 编号 (不是物理引脚！)\nPWM 脚: 12, 13, 19, 26 (电机速度)\nGPIO 脚: 5, 6, 17, 18, 22, 23, 24, 25\nI2C/SDA/SCL: 保留",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "strokeColor": "#495057",
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "originalText": "BCM 编号 (不是物理引脚！)\nPWM 脚: 12, 13, 19, 26 (电机速度)\nGPIO 脚: 5, 6, 17, 18, 22, 23, 24, 25\nI2C/SDA/SCL: 保留",
      "autoResize": true
    },
