     "strokeColor":"#0c8599","strokeWidth":2,
     "boundElements":[{"id":"t_cameras","type":"text"}]},
    {"type":"text","id":"t_cameras","x":1670,"y":460,"width":340,"height":25,
     "text":"摄像头 & 音频","fontSize":18,"fontFamily":1,
     "strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","textAlign":"center","verticalAlign":"middle",
     "containerId":"bg_cameras","originalText":"摄像头 & 音频","autoResize":true},
    {"type":"text","id":"cameras_pins","x":1675,"y":510,"width":330,"height":100,
     "text":"CSI 摄像头 → CSI-2 排线接口\n  (云台舵机上，可转动)\nUSB 摄像头+麦 → USB 接口\n小喇叭 → 3.5mm 音频口",
     "fontSize":16,"fontFamily":1,"strokeColor":"#495057","textAlign":"left",
     "verticalAlign":"top",
     "originalText":"CSI 摄像头 → CSI-2 排线接口\n  (云台舵机上，可转动)\nUSB 摄像头+麦 → USB 接口\n小喇叭 → 3.5mm 音频口","autoResize":true},

    {"type":"rectangle","id":"bg_power","x":1660,"y":680,"width":360,"height":140,
     "roundness":{"type":3},"backgroundColor":"#ffc9c9","fillStyle":"solid",
     "strokeColor":"#c92a2a","strokeWidth":2,
     "boundElements":[{"id":"t_power","type":"text"}]},
    {"type":"text","id":"t_power","x":1670,"y":690,"width":340,"height":25,
     "text":"⚡ 电源系统","fontSize":20,"fontFamily":1,
     "strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","textAlign":"center","verticalAlign":"middle",
     "containerId":"bg_power","originalText":"⚡ 电源系统","autoResize":true},
    {"type":"text","id":"power_pins","x":1675,"y":740,"width":330,"height":60,
     "text":"L298N 两块共用外接电源 6-12V\n树莓派用官方 5V 3A 电源\n舵机/摄像头从树莓派 5V 取电",
     "fontSize":16,"fontFamily":1,"strokeColor":"#495057","textAlign":"left",
     "verticalAlign":"top",
     "originalText":"L298N 两块共用外接电源 6-12V\n树莓派用官方 5V 3A 电源\n舵机/摄像头从树莓派 5V 取电","autoResize":true},

    {"type":"rectangle","id":"bg_notes","x":80,"y":680,"width":500,"height":140,
     "roundness":{"type":3},"backgroundColor":"#fff3bf","fillStyle":"solid",
     "strokeColor":"#e67700","strokeWidth":2,
     "boundElements":[{"id":"t_notes","type":"text"}]},
    {"type":"text","id":"t_notes","x":90,"y":690,"width":480,"height":25,
     "text":"⚠ 重要提示","fontSize":20,"fontFamily":1,
     "strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","textAlign":"center","verticalAlign":"middle",
     "containerId":"bg_notes","originalText":"⚠ 重要提示","autoResize":true},
    {"type":"text","id":"notes_pins","x":95,"y":730,"width":470,"height":80,
     "text":"1. HY-SRF05 ECHO 脚(5V)必须分压后再接 GPIO 16\n2. L298N 逻辑输入 3.3V 兼容，可直接接树莓派\n3. 所有 GND 必须共地（树莓派 + L298N + 外接电源）\n4. 舵机线序: 棕(GND) 红(VCC 5V) 橙(信号)",
     "fontSize":16,"fontFamily":1,"strokeColor":"#495057","textAlign":"left",
     "verticalAlign":"top",
     "originalText":"1. HY-SRF05 ECHO 脚(5V)必须分压后再接 GPIO 16\n2. L298N 逻辑输入 3.3V 兼容，可直接接树莓派\n3. 所有 GND 必须共地（树莓派 + L298N + 外接电源）\n4. 舵机线序: 棕(GND) 红(VCC 5V) 橙(信号)","autoResize":true},

    {"type":"text","id":"footer",
     "x":620,"y":880,"width":600,"height":24,
     "text":"所有 GPIO 编号为 BCM 模式，非物理引脚编号！",
     "fontSize":16,"fontFamily":1,"strokeColor":"#e03131",
     "textAlign":"center","verticalAlign":"middle",
     "originalText":"所有 GPIO 编号为 BCM 模式，非物理引脚编号！","autoResize":true}
